<p>

<b>Jeremy Brett</b> (3 November 1933 – 12 September 1995), born <b>Peter Jeremy William Huggins</b>,  was an <country wordnetid="108544813" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../316/9316.xml">
English</link></country>
 <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../753/753.xml">
