<sec>
<st>
Early life</st>
<p>

Brett was born at Berkswell Grange in <site wordnetid="108651247" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../078/3109078.xml">
Berkswell</link></site>
, <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../648/383648.xml">
Warwickshire</link>, <country wordnetid="108544813" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../316/9316.xml">
England</link></country>
, <autocracy wordnetid="108361001" confidence="0.8">
<system wordnetid="108435388" confidence="0.8">
<social_group wordnetid="107950920" confidence="0.8">
<political_orientation wordnetid="106212839" confidence="0.8">
