</written_communication>
</play>
</dramatic_composition>
</it>, making him one of only three actors to play both Holmes and Watson professionally (the other two are <person wordnetid="100007846" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<actor wordnetid="109765278" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../471/3870471.xml">
